snippet.title: Alila Medical Media
snippet.description:
We are known for producing simple and clear mini lectures, perfect for students, teachers and patient education. You are welcome to post a link to or embed (using Youtube embed function) our Youtube videos on your websites or for lecture presentation - In this case your viewers essentially watch the videos on our Youtube channel, with ads. If however you need to download the videos for independent uses, you should purchase a license from our website: https://www.alilamedicalmedia.com/  You will get to download non-watermarked videos with license purchase.
All images/videos by Alila Medical Media are for information purposes ONLY and are NOT intended to replace professional medical advice, diagnosis or treatment. 
If our videos are helpful to you, please consider supporting us on Patreon. As a token of our appreciation, we also offer early video access and free image downloads in return: https://www.patreon.com/AlilaMedicalMedia/posts
